          <h3 class="text-black text-base font-semibold mb-1">Judgment before automation</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-sm leading-relaxed">Not everything should be automated. We're deliberate about what stays human — and why. Restraint is part of what you're hiring.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-linen rounded-[10px] p-5 border-2 text-center" style="border-color: #001D52;">
          <h3 class="text-black text-base font-semibold mb-1">Clarity over complexity</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-sm leading-relaxed">If a system can't be explained simply, it isn't finished. Every workflow we build can be understood by the people who use it.</p>
