        <div class="mb-10"></div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-black text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
          <p class="text-black italic">Clients describe it as calm.</p>
          <p>There are no status meetings held for the sake of appearances.<br />No performative reporting designed to justify the invoice. No<br />pressure to expand scope beyond what makes sense.</p>
          <p>You'll always know what we're doing and why. Decisions<br />are explained, not handed down. Progress is visible, not<br />summarized at the end of the month.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Callout box -->
        <div class="flex items-stretch justify-center gap-4 mt-10">
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
          <p class="text-black text-sm italic leading-relaxed py-1 text-center">We build what needs to exist — and stop.</p>
          <div class="w-0.5 bg-navy rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></div>
